reviewText: why was this even made again ...who cares waste of film lol but hey everyone has a dream go for it XD

This is a good & fun movie, I recommend it to anyone who likes a good Grind house Horror flick movie with lots of gore, The only problem I had with this newer release is that the Blu-Ray has a purple back so it's a burn, But the regular DVD is a silverback, so if your thinking blu ray , You'd be better off with the original release or the DVD version Of Lucy's revenge Avoid the Blu Ray unless you don't mind a burned copy, or excuse me a professionaly  made purple back lol.
